{"tid":1279593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"煙霧彈真相  「有片」 示威者有鬼 大家幫手頂","createTime":"2019-07-02T17:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T17:05:33.000Z","uid":47216,"like":0,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8b189575251f552e9d2e9194016ff8fec2f259a7","tid":1279593,"uid":47216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:01:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m0a62ERwtqM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm0a62ERwtqM&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRcyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=9ee9e124\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m0a62ERwtqM</a><br />\n<br />\n煙霧彈 2:14 <br />\n<br />\n我明白這次有死士<br />\n但死士不應該這樣逃離<br />\nIt doesn&rsquo;t make senses.<br />\n<br />\n加上警方的手錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次我哋冇中計<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95pWXfY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95pWXfY.png&h=8de9c622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係我哋今次中咗伏<br />\n<br />\n「香港人的惡夢其實剛剛開始，因為林鄭背後最近出現了這樣的一個高手。強調，是一個，只有一個，但這人的腦袋是政府上下幾萬人加起來也及不上的一個腦袋。<br />\n<br />\n設下的空城計，凌晨四時的記者會，甚至之前警察總部被圍也刻意按耐著不使出來的武力，通通都是來自一個腦袋。<br />\n<br />\n此人有名有姓，但恕我不能再說更多。只是希望大家知道，我們現在的對手，不僅懂得把玩政治，而且更視操控民心為一場證明自己轉數很高的遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n為了不讓站在同一陣線的朋友白白犧牲，我們在往後的日子必定要冷靜下來才能力挽狂瀾。<br />\n<br />\n要力挽狂瀾，用力是不夠的」 -葉朗晴<br />\n<br />\n大家小心！"},{"pid":"65d944264b815bddec9f2ed57dd7fce71869ceb7","tid":1279593,"uid":47216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:01:50.000Z","msg":"頂"},{"pid":"0dea94d76835093d50c66e1b19b5dbf4321984fb","tid":1279593,"uid":47216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:02:01.000Z","msg":"頂"},{"pid":"3222719f09e5fe246b7be3413fa032b796d336d4","tid":1279593,"uid":47216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:02:14.000Z","msg":"頂"},{"pid":"50b1aeec